  "texts": [
    "These attacks become possible when an application processes insecure data from users.",
    "During this attack, the attacker's provided operating system commands are typically executed with permission from the vulnerable application.",
    "The consequences of command injection attacks can vary from compromising data confidentiality and integrity to gaining unauthorized remote access to the system that hosts the vulnerable application [105,106].",
    "Physical threatsPhysical threats in IoT security refer to risks and dangers that arise from physical.",
    "Access to IoT devices, systems, or infrastructure."
